"By using eizsole.lv, you agree to these terms. The platform provides a "
"marketplace for posting listings and running auctions. The platform is not a "
"party to transactions between buyers and sellers."

#: templates/listings/terms.html:14
msgid "2. Reģistrācija"
msgstr "2. Registration"

#: templates/listings/terms.html:16
msgid "Reģistrācijai nepieciešams derīgs e-pasts un tālrunis."
msgstr "A valid email and phone number are required for registration."

