"kvalitāti, piegādes laiku vai citiem darījuma aspektiem. Lietotāji paši ir "
"atbildīgi par darījuma drošību."
msgstr ""
"The platform assumes no liability for transactions between users, product "
"quality, delivery times, or other aspects of the transaction. Users are "
"personally responsible for transaction safety."

